sources.title: La baby sitter
sources.description: Title: La baby sitter Summary: A naive young girl is forcefully kidnapped while babysitting the son of a wealthy food mogul. Her and the boy are held hostage by an ex-stuntman and a vengeful movie star. Directed by: René Clément Actors: Directed by René Clément. With Maria Schneider, Sydne Rome, Vic Morrow Production Company: Cité Films Release Date: 15 October 1975 (France) A naive young girl is forcefully kidnapped while babysitting the son of a wealthy food mogul. Her and the boy are held hostage by an ex-stuntman and a vengeful movie star.
